sentences: Antonio Faraò (born January 19, 1965) is an Italian jazz pianist.
A native of Rome, Italy, Faraò earned a degree in 1983 from the Giuseppe Verdi Conservatory in Milan and performed in clubs as a teenager.
Enja released his debut album, Black Inside, in 1999.
